{"tid":1214350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你以為送中就完喇咩？","createTime":"2019-06-13T04:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:05:17.000Z","uid":181035,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32e2a04564c263103902cba46b091e3228181204","tid":1214350,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">長話短說，發夢聽到朋友識人係立法會做，佢話我知：<br />\n<br />\n政府已經plan好送中過左之後就接住強推國歌法，<br />\n<br />\n日期都定埋係23號，就算唔係嗰日都肯定係接住送中即刻出，<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得送中就算，仲陸續有黎！！<br />\n<br />\n我知大家好辛苦，好挫折，我都係，<br />\n<br />\n但都求大家唔好放棄，唔好諗會唔會成功，<br />\n<br />\n係保存到自身嘅情況下，做到幾多得幾多，<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻放棄嘅話，以後都只會俾共匪㩒住黎砌，<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！！！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申：尋日都有出，夜晚失眠瞓下又醒下咁，難得咁都夢到朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d8529d86b479f009d04640dde7d8d62722ed6ec0","tid":1214350,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"照舊啦，硬碰唔得就癱鐵封路<br />\n玩到佢屈服"},{"pid":"faa4a33857d4a95f11f665f823d2af3f681cfc36","tid":1214350,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8529d86b479f009d04640dde7d8d62722ed6ec0","tid":1214350,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"照舊啦，硬碰唔得就癱鐵封路<br />\n玩到佢屈服"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:15:42.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得應該硬碰<br />\n依家對黑驚做咩都唔會有人覺得有問題"},{"pid":"b7fedd66d36ed6c81db92899dc25e3f1bb962465","tid":1214350,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T04:16:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f081d41d5730201169e69da19b25356259355ba0","tid":1214350,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faa4a33857d4a95f11f665f823d2af3f681cfc36","tid":1214350,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8529d86b479f009d04640dde7d8d62722ed6ec0","tid":1214350,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited